{"article_id":"en0Zhw65Ryzn7xOl","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The budget","depth":6},{"id":1,"text":"that the Trump administration will roll out Tuesday","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"does much more than balance in 10 years","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"and boost military spending ;","depth":6},{"id":4,"text":"it forces a major change in the way","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"Washington looks at the spending","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"by putting the focus on taxpayers instead payees .","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"President Trump ' s team went through the budget line by line with a simple question :","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Would taxpayers want their money spent on this ?","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"Turns out that plenty of times the answer was \" No . \"","depth":7},{"id":10,"text":"The result was $ 3.6 trillion in cuts over 10 years","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"- the most ever proposed by a U.S. president -","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"to reach balance in 2027","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"without touching Medicare or Social Security retirement benefits ,","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"as Mr. Trump promised .","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"Still , cuts to education , social welfare and other programs","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"while increasing defense spending by $ 54 billion","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"raised eyebrows on Capitol Hill .","depth":6},{"id":18,"text":"Mick Mulvaney , the president ' s budget director , called it a \" taxpayer-first budget . \"","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"With the U.S. carrying a $ 20 trillion debt ,","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"he said ,","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"there is no excuse","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"for continuing to pay for feel-good programs","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"that don ' t work .","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"\" We can not continue to simply measure our compassion or our success by the amount of money","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"we spend .","depth":9},{"id":26,"text":"We are going to measure our compassion and success","depth":9},{"id":27,"text":"by actually helping people","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"and by respecting taxpayers","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"who pay for it in the first place , \"","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"For the budget ' s math to work ,","depth":4},{"id":32,"text":"the Trump administration relies on increasing economic growth to 3 percent ,","depth":5},{"id":33,"text":"which is an ambitious goal above the 1.9 percent average of the past decade .","depth":5},{"id":34,"text":"Mr. Trump ' s plans","depth":5},{"id":35,"text":"to reform spending , taxes , welfare and federal regulations","depth":5},{"id":36,"text":"are all geared toward restoring the 3 percent growth","depth":5},{"id":37,"text":"that had been the norm in the U.S. since World War II .","depth":5},{"id":38,"text":"Like every other presidential budget , Mr. Trump ' s spending plan documents his priorities","depth":5},{"id":39,"text":"but will be pronounced dead on arrival in Congress .","depth":5},{"id":40,"text":"But this budget , more than others , has opened the negotiations from a new vantage point .","depth":4},{"id":41,"text":"Democrats slammed the budget","depth":7},{"id":42,"text":"as soon as details leaked out .","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"\" Instead of protecting public education , health insurance and other programs","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"that help working Americans ,","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"President Trump is simply committed to make room for his massive tax cut for the rich , \"","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"said Democratic National Committee spokeswoman Adrienne Watson .","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"Lawrence Mishel , president of the liberal Economic Policy Institute , was taken aback .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"\" This is ludicrous , \"","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"\" If they think","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"they know what the voters want ,","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"which is what they are claiming now ,","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"then why didn ' t they explain it to voters","depth":10},{"id":54,"text":"when it could affect their vote ? \"","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"\" It ' s a flimflam","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"and it ' s unseemly , \"","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"\" It ' s wrong for America ,","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"and I think","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that it is a betrayal to working-class Americans . \"","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"White House officials argued","depth":6},{"id":62,"text":"that the spending cuts made good on Mr. Trump ' s pledge","depth":7},{"id":63,"text":"to reduce the size of the federal workforce and create a leaner , less-intrusive and more-effective government .","depth":7},{"id":64,"text":"\" People don ' t mind paying their taxes","depth":8},{"id":65,"text":"as long as they know","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"their money is not being wasted","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"and for too long ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"I think ,","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"the government has not been able to prove to them","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"that that ' s the case , \"","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"said Mr. Mulvaney .","depth":6},{"id":72,"text":"Pushing Mr. Trump ' s priorities ,","depth":5},{"id":73,"text":"the budget increases military , law enforcement and border security spending .","depth":5},{"id":74,"text":"It allots $ 2.6 billion for new border security infrastructure and technology ,","depth":5},{"id":75,"text":"including $ 1.6 billion for new and replaced wall construction along the border with Mexico .","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"The crackdown on illegal immigration took other forms in the budget .","depth":6},{"id":77,"text":"The taxpayer-first review resulted in a proposal","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"to require people","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"receiving the earned income tax credit and child tax credit","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"to have a Social Security number .","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"The change would prevent illegal immigrants from pocketing the refundable tax credits","depth":10},{"id":82,"text":"designed to help poor families ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"saving $ 40 billion over 10 years .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Those and other welfare reforms would save $ 274 billion over 10 years .","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"Other cuts are aimed at prodding people on food stamps and Social Security disability insurance back into the workforce .","depth":7},{"id":86,"text":"Mr. Mulvaney said","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"getting able-bodied Americans off disability benefits didn ' t break Mr. Trump ' s promise","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"not to cut Social Security .","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"He said","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"voters understood the promise to be about retirement benefits .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"Other cuts ,","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"contributing to a 2 percent reduction in nondefense spending each year ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"included :","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"⦁ A $ 800 billion cut from Medicaid spending over 10 years","depth":9},{"id":95,"text":"that is part of the House-passed Republican bill","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"to replace Obamacare .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"⦁ Zeroing out the heating assistance program for the poor for a $ 3 billion savings .","depth":9},{"id":98,"text":"⦁ Reducing food stamps by $ 193 billion , or 25 percent , over 10 years .","depth":9},{"id":99,"text":"Chris Edwards , director of tax policy studies at the libertarian Cato Institute and editor of DownsizingGovernment.org , said","depth":7},{"id":100,"text":"the new budget perspective was long overdue .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"He noted","depth":7},{"id":102,"text":"that the earned income tax credit has a 25 percent fraud rate ,","depth":8},{"id":103,"text":"according to government data .","depth":8},{"id":104,"text":"\" Congress has known this ,","depth":8},{"id":105,"text":"but they don ' t seem to be able to solve the problem , \"","depth":8},{"id":106,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":107,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"Mulvaney is being more aggressive in pushing reforms .","depth":9},{"id":109,"text":"He is the most fiscally conservative budget director","depth":9},{"id":110,"text":"that I can remember in the last three decades , \"","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"said Mr. Edwards .","depth":7}],"relations":[{"parent":223,"left":149,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":149,"left":142,"right":148,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":142,"left":118,"right":141,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":118,"left":115,"right":117,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":115,"left":113,"right":114,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":113,"left":0,"right":1,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":114,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":117,"left":116,"right":6,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":116,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":141,"left":128,"right":140,"relation":"evaluation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":125,"right":127,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":125,"left":120,"right":124,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":120,"left":119,"right":9,"relation":"topic","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":119,"left":7,"right":8,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":124,"left":121,"right":123,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":123,"left":12,"right":122,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":127,"left":126,"right":17,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":126,"left":15,"right":16,"relation":"joint","nuclear